A STEEL INDUSTRIALS KERALA LTD. V. CAPT. S.M. REBELLO & ORS [1985] INSC 36; AIR 1985 SC 760; 1985 (2) SCR 998; 1985 (2) SCC 363; 1985 (1) SCALE 289 (26 February 1985)

 FAZALALI, SYED MURTAZA FAZALALI, SYED MURTAZA VARADARAJAN, A. (J) 
CITATION: 1985 AIR 760 1985 SCR (2) 998 1985 SCC (2) 363 1985 SCALE (1)289 
ACT:
 Term appointment for a fixed period-Premature termination of services of a Master of the ship-Whether the "master of a ship" is a "seaman" within the meaning of the provision of the Merchant Shipping Act, 1958 for the purpose of entitlement to get full compensation on the termination of his services, for the entire period of his contract- Section 3(22), 3(42), 89, 101,103,118,120,125,143,148,178,to 183 of the Merchant Shipping Act, 1958-Whether the contract of appointment of a master of a ship and the owner is the nature of a contract of personal service and therefore cannot be specifically enforced.
 
